  Cha2 jit8 Lam5 Bi2-chiu u7 sio2 kok, siok8 Se-pan-ga5 koan2 e5 si5, toe7-hng bo5 an-cheng7, koaN-hu2 si3-koe3 liah8 chok-loan7 e5 thau5, chit8 e5 Eng-kok lang5 iah8 siu7 liah8, iau2 be7 ke3 tng5 chiu7 teng7 i e5 choe7. Chit-e5 Eng-kok lang5 bat jip8 Bi2-kok chek8, sou2-i2 Bi2-kok leng2-su7-koaN thiaN--kiN3, siuN7 tioh8 khi3 ka7 i pang3, sou2 choe3 long2 bo5 chhai2 kang. Bo5 loa7 ku2 Eng-kok leng2-su7-koaN chai iah8 tioh8-kip, khi3 chhe7 toe7-hng-koaN kong2, “Peh-siN3 hoan7-hoat, be7 ke3 tng5, chaiN2-iuN7 teng7 i si2 choe7? Na7 an2-ni choe3, pe3-kok cheng3-hu2 tek-khak kap li2 kau-siap8.” Toe7-hng-koaN boe7 beng5 kau-siap8 e5 toa7 koan-he7, pang3 choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2. Kau3 bou2 jit8 beh chhoa7 hoan7-lang5 khi3 phah chheng3, koaN toa3 tui7 khan hoan7-lang5 kau3 siaN5-piN, khau3 i e5 kha-chhiu2, hou7 i the siaN5-chhiuN5, tui3-bin7 khia7 chit8 e5 kiah8 chheng3 e5 peng, teh theng3-hau7 koaN-tiuN2 chhut “Khui chheng3” e5 ho7-leng7. Hut-jian5 Eng Bi2 nng7 kok e5 leng2-su7-koaN koaN2 kau3, chit8 e5 kiah8 chit8 ki kok-ki5, jia hoan7-lang5 e5 sin-khu, toa7 siaN ka7 kiah8 chheng3 e5 peng kong2, “Li2 kaN2 khui chheng3, bu2-ban7 goan2 e5 kok-ki5--mah?” Kiah8 chheng3 e5 peng thiaN-kiN3 chit ho7 oe7, chheng3 m7-kaN2 khui, toe7-hng-koaN put-tek-i2 kio3 kiah8 chheng3 e5 peng khi3, chiong hoan7-lang5 sang3 kau leng2-su7-koaN, chiau3 in pun2-kok e5 hoat-lut8 pan7-li2. 
