  Tng Na2-a e5 si5, toa7 chui2 biat8 se3-kan, hit si5 lang5 sou2 tiam3 e5 toe7-ui7 chi2 u7 nng7 khoan2. (1) Chun5-lai7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 lang5. (2) Chun5-goa7 hou7 chui2 im-si2 e5 lang5. I2-goa7 bo5 sou2-chai7 thang hou7 hit si5 e5 lang5 tiam3. Ia5-sou siat phi3-ju7 kong2, tho2 hi5 e5 lang5 pha-tioh8 hi5, “Keng2 ho2--e5 he7 loh8 khah-a2, phaiN2--e5 hiat-kak8 khi3.” Koh kong2, “Chap8 e5 chai7-sek-lu2 ngia5-chih sin kiaN2-sai3, chit8 poaN3 gong7--e5, chit8 poaN3 gau5--e5. Gau5--e5 hou7 chu2-lang5 chiap-lap8 jip8 chhu3, gong7--e5 ku7-choat8 ti7 goa7-bin7 boe7 tit jip8.” Tai7-khai3 chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 e5 i3-su3. Seng3-keng put-chi2 choe7 sou2-chai7 u7 kong2-khi2, long2-chong2 si7 phi3-ju7 se3-kan lang5 sou2 tiam3 e5 toe7-ui7 chi2 u7 nng7 khoan2. (1) Thian-tong5. (2) Te7-gek8. I2-goa7 bo5 te7 saN khoan2 e5 toe7-ui7 thang tiam3. 
