  An2-ni chiau3 goa7-mau7 khoaN3 si7 kek8 ki5 tui3-tiong7 to7-li2, ui7-tioh8 kau3-hoe7 jiat8-sim chhut-lat8, chong2-si7 soe3-ji7 ka7 i chha5-kho2, i e5 sim oan5-choan5 bo5 hap8 Ki-tok saN-lian5. Ki-tok kong2, “Kio3 goa2 choe3 Chu2--e5, bo5 tek-khak tak8 e5 jip8 Thian-kok, tok8-tok8 chun-than3 ThiN-pe7 e5 chi2-i3 e5 lang5 oe7 jip8.“ “Tng sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5, tek-khak u7 lang5 kong2, goa2 kiam2 m7 si7 hong7 Kiu3 Chu2 e5 mia5 thoan5-to7 koaN2-kui2, kiaN5 tak8 hang7 ki5-koai3 e5 tai7-chi3 kap sin5-jiah--mah? Chu2 siaN2-su7 m7-jin7 goa2?” Goa2 tek-khak in3 kong2, “Lin2 long2 si7 choe3 phaiN2 e5 lang5, tioh8 kin2-kin2 khi3, goa2 m7-bat lin2.” TaN Kau3-hoe7 lai7 u7 lang5, chhui3 chheng-hou Kiu3 Chu2, sim-lai7 bo5 kap Kiu3 Chu2 saN-lian5, sou2 kong2 sou2 kiaN5 bo5 kap seng3-to7 saN-hap8, chit ho7 lang5 thai2-tho2 u7 thang ng3-bang7 jip8 Thian-kok, bian2-tit te7-gek8 e5 heng5-hoat8. Sit8-chai7 chin gui5-hiam2. 
  ThiN-e7 Kan u7 Chit Ho7 Pan7-gi5 Su7--Mah? 
  Chit8 e5 bok8-su khia7-khi2 oa2-kun7 thou5-thoaN3 khong3. Tak8 pai2 kau3 chiah8 jit8-tau3 e5 si5, i chiu7 jip8 khong3-lai7 thoan5 Hok-im hou7 choe3 kang lang5 thiaN. Jip8 khong3 e5 khang khoan2-sit chhin-chhiuN7 chiN2, tui3 teng2-bin7 kau3 khong3-toe2, u7 pah goa7 tng7 chhim. Chu2-lang5 u7 pi7-pan7 ki-khi3, oe7 chiuN7 oe7 loh8, thang chiuN7 thou5-thoaN3 chhut khong3, bian2 eng7 lang5 e5 lat8, put-chi2 li7-pian7. Khong3-lai7 sou2-chai7 put-chi2 khui-khoah, oe7 iong5-un2 kang2 chheng lang5 ti7 lai7-bin7 ong2-lai5 choe3-kang. 
